# Insulin Aspart Protamine

## Overview

Intermediate-acting insulin analog providing delayed absorption through protamine crystallization.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Aspart Protamine |

## Mechanism of Action

Protamine-bound aspart insulin forms crystals that dissolve slowly providing extended glucose control beyond regular aspart.

